{"tid":1771651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲記唔記得幾時開始嗌光復香港","createTime":"2019-12-06T04:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T05:20:05.000Z","uid":220182,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8ec8ef14660926b9edbba08d06633f71cd96651b","tid":1771651,"uid":220182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"6月份，香港人上街<br />\n嗌嘅係反送中、徹回、林鄭下台、沒有暴徒，只有暴政<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要真普選間中先會聽到，連和應都比較少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果當時林鄭真係即時徹回同下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信好多人都會收貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係，廣東茂名嘅人同6月嘅我哋差唔多<br />\n只要政府還一個公道就會收貨<br />\n一開始大部分人唔可以即刻反思問題到制度上面<br />\n你話茂名同我哋本質唔同，當然係唔同<br />\n咁我哋依家嘅本質又咪當初嘅反送中咁簡單?<br />\n<br />\n支爆果頭近，令民眾不滿嘅事只會陸續有黎<br />\n連登風向係唔好隨便Connect，本質唔同的確唔可以<br />\n但係成功令佢哋反思制度問題，繼而改革，先叫真Connect<br />\n<br />\n多謝你睇到呢度，其實只係算支線<br />\n主線: 12 8維園3點 已出不反 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O1peRhD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO1peRhD.jpg&h=6a38c125&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc6ba95de27c4330aebc3fa233eec9d8c35680e6","tid":1771651,"uid":16374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f77eac592db21120fc80444da4bfef5764eac2","tid":1771651,"uid":1988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc6ba95de27c4330aebc3fa233eec9d8c35680e6","tid":1771651,"uid":16374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:34:15.000Z","msg":"我到而家都會發夢諗起721嘅上環"},{"pid":"d45b2e78bc3a9e9653c6b3b46ce898a661343fe8","tid":1771651,"uid":328114,"like":1